summary:
Adds a portion of a dungeon.
Made for play testing. Contains playable areas only.
Play time : around 10~30min
Serious planning was done, and testing it out to figure out if it is engaging.
descriptionHtml:
This is part of my level design. 
Even though the level design is still in development, I thought that this portion of it is at a playable state. 
So I cut off all the unfinished parts and made this for testing. 

See the video to preview the map

-Notice- 
- You need the latest update and Dragonborn DLC to play it. 
- Your character must have learned whirlwind sprint to play it. 
- It is still under construction. 
- Please leave a comment if you found any bugs. 
- Any suggestions along with feedback would be greatly appreciated.
